      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GEORDIE LAD (8) has a strong overall record having six wins and 13 places from 25 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (22.82) over 400m at this track. Has never been out of the money in four starts this course and distance. Drawn wide but with a clean break will be tough to beat again. RAPIDO KUNA (7) could not have been more impressive last start in his an outstanding 27.29 win at this track over 488m. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. SUNSET OYSTER (5) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind RAPIDO KUNA (28.01) in a Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Can measure up. INCREDIBLE HEART (1) generally performs well from this box.",
